subject: Horse Racing
organizations: New York Stallion Stakes Cab Calloway Division
lead_paragraph: Uncle T Seven made a last-to-first run to win the New York Stallion Stakes Cab Calloway Division for 3-year-old colts and geldings by two and a quarter lengths.
